message:
I'm kinda tired of all the generic characters people make using the "Unknown" character creator, so I'm sharing my own! This is the "Refined Character Creator" - a culmination of multiple Character Template bot formats I've enjoyed.

It will detect wether you're creating an OC or a pre-existing character from media, and can even read urls! The format is easy to read, and easier to edit.

Enjoy!

(THIS BOT IS LARGELY SFW, BUT HAS SOME POTENTIAL NSFW CATEGORIES SUCH AS "GENITALS", "BUST", AND "SEXUALITY". Simply edit these out if you don't want them represented.)

Here's the link: https://perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Refined_Character_Creator~fe7e0cce450e2d06eb4e0036673f93e3.gz
